name: Catgirl Optimus
description: What is $OPTIG? Catgirl Optimus is a community-driven project, made to pay homage to Elon Musk's vision of a Catgirl Optimus Robot, through the blockchain. How many $OPTIG coins are there in circulation? Catgirl Optimus launched with an initial, fixed circulating supply of 1,000,000,000 tokens. This number is deflationary, as $OPTIG contract contains an automatic token burn feature. $OPTIG vision: Catgirl Optimus aims to create brand awareness and perpetuate the narrative of the Catgirl Optimus AI bot; eventually becoming a top cryptocurrency and being recognized as such. By utilizing means of organic growth, marketing, and social media exposure, $OPTIG aims to be recognized by and provide Elon Musk with ideas for the Catgirl version of Optimus AI bot.
